#, fuzzy
msgid "All three transports -- JSON-RPC, gRPC, and HTTP+JSON/REST -- are fully supported and considered equal. Just pick the artifact(s) for the transport(s) you need."
msgstr "所有三种传输方式（JSON-RPC、gRPC 和 HTTP+JSON/REST）都完全支持，并被视为同等重要。您只需为所需的传输方式选择相应的工具即可。"

