#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The biggest addition is the Integration Test Kit (ITK) -- a configurable Quarkus-based A2A agent that runs predefined scenarios from the ITK test harness to validate protocol compliance across different SDK implementations (Java, Python, TypeScript, etc.). This gives us confidence that the Java SDK interoperates correctly with agents built using other A2A SDKs."
