#, fuzzy
msgid "*Android HTTP client* -- `AndroidA2AHttpClient` using `HttpURLConnection` makes the SDK usable on Android (https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-cr1-released/[1.0.0.CR1])"
msgstr "使用 `HttpURLConnection` 的 *Android HTTP 客户端* - `AndroidA2AHttpClient` 使 SDK 可在 Android 上使用（ link:https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-cr1-released/[1.0.0.CR1）]"

#. type: Plain text
